 중간;mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-font-width:95%;letter-spacing:-0.5pt;font-size:14.0pt;\">이 있다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-ascii-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-font-width:95%;letter-spacing:-0.5pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:14.0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-font-width:95%;letter-spacing:-0.5pt;font-size:14.0pt;\">그래서 그 명칭 자체를 비성경적인 것으로 여겨 거부한다</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-ascii-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-font-width:95%;letter-spacing:-0.5pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:14.0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-font-width:95%;letter-spacing:-0.5pt;font-size:14.0pt;\">그러나 </span><u><span style=\"font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-font-width:95%;letter-spacing:-0.5pt;font-size:14.0pt;\">멤버십은 매우 성경적이다</span></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-ascii-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-font-width:95%;letter-spacing:-0.5pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:14.0pt;\">. </span></p><p class=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;mso-pagination:none;text-autospace:none;mso-padding-alt:0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-font-width:95%;letter-spacing:-0.5pt;font-size:14.0pt;\">성경은 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-ascii-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-font-width:95%;letter-spacing:-0.5pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0pt;\">‘</span><span style=\"font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-font-width:95%;letter-spacing:-0.5pt;font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0pt;\">성도</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;font-family:마루 부리OTF 중간;mso-ascii-font-family:마루 부